    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    DescriptionPanel
    GUI panel for displaying and editing image descriptions.
    FileNode
    Represents a file node for graphical interfaces with name, path and expansion state.
    FolderExplorerPanel
    A panel that displays a folder and image file explorer using a tree view.
    FolderExplorerPanel.SelectionListener
    Interface for handling selection events.
    FolderExplorerPanelTest
    Unit tests for FolderExplorerPanel class.
    FolderGenerator
    Utility class for generating random folder structures.
    ImageAnalyzer
    Class for analyzing image files.
    ImageCreator
    Utility class for creating images with random geometric shapes.
    ImageCreator.Format
    Supported image output formats.
    ImageInfo
    Class representing image data and basic file information.
    ImageOperations
    Provides basic image manipulation operations including loading, saving and resizing.
    ImagePanel
    Custom panel for displaying images with automatic scaling.
    ImagePreviewPanel
    Panel for previewing and editing images with various operations including: - Zooming in/out - Cropping - Resizing - Adjusting brightness, contrast and saturation - Adding descriptions - Saving modified images
    ImagePreviewPanel.ImageModifiedListener
    Listener interface for image modification events.
    ImagePreviewPanelTest
    Unit tests for the ImagePreviewPanel class.
    ImageTablePanel
    Panel that displays a table of image files with their technical specifications.
    ImageTablePanel.ImageSelectionListener
    Interface for receiving image selection and rename events.
    Main
    Main class that launches the image library application.
    MainWindow
    Main application window for the Image Library system.
    MetadataEditor
    Utility class for reading and writing image metadata (EXIF).
    SimplePaintDialog
    A simple painting dialog that allows users to draw images.
